  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      10 patients with chronic heart failure receiving daptomycin therapy after implantation of a
      left ventricular heart assist system. Measurement of daptomycin levels in drainage fluids
      (mediastinal and pleural drainage systems) and in blood samples.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
